{
  "stem": "25639.8",
  "chunk_idx": 9,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 12.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "And one woman took a handful of macaroni and plopped it into her skirt or dress, and-- and the same thing with just plain sugar.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "That's odd, I thought.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "All this time in the camp, and-- camps, I've never seen anything like it.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Oh, what to do, what to do.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So I decided to quickly pick up the raw macaroni, at least.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "The sugar was a total loss.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] And at that point, I was beaten unconscious for holding up the line.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "There was no rhyme or reason for this or that.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We just had to accept what was dished out to us, I mean physically and in every other respect, as well.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So I really would have died there had-- had not some of my fellow prisoners still been capable of human feelings and compassion.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I was told later that they half-dragged and half carried me back to the box car.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I came to when I heard a voice, a man's voice.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And it said, we are-- you are lucky, he said.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "It was one of our German guards, but we were already on a regular train.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "It was not a boxcar.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "I have no idea how I-- how I got on it or where I got on it.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "For many, many years, until we had a reunion a few years ago in Ravensbruck, I used to think-- well, this is what I remembered until then.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "That-- that this guard, I remember seeing him.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "He said that you are lucky because you are free, but I have to turn around and go back and face the music.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And I thought, that's strange.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "No, they were about to kill me.",
      "word_count": 7
    }
  ],
